    {
      "id": "verify-fn-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 383,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "ReceiptStore.verify_chain(channel_id)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#065F46",
      "roughness": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "verify-steps",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 410,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 155,
      "text": "for each receipt in chain[channel_id]:\n\n  1. Verify signature\n     → ecrecover(EIP-191(sha256(receipt))) == sender\n\n  2. Verify hash linkage\n     → receipt.prev_hash == sha256(previous_receipt)\n\n  3. Verify ordering\n     → receipt.nonce == previous.nonce + 1\n     → receipt.amount >= previous.amount (cumulative)\n\n  4. Verify genesis\n     → chain[0].prev_hash == 0x00..00 (32 zero bytes)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#065F46",
      "roughness": 0
    },

